==English==
===Etymology===
From Russian [[Запорожье]] (Zaporozhye), a city in southeast Ukraine.

===Adjective===
'''Zaporozhye'''

#of or from the city of Zaporozhye, [[Ukraine]]; of the kind or style prevalent in Zaporozhye.
:capital of ''Zaporizhzhya'' region ([[Запорiжжя]]), Ukraine<br>—''Columbia Encyclopedia''<sup>[http://www.bartleby.com/65/za/Zaporizh.html]</sup>

